overview.en: BBT is a universal point for BBT ecological distribution. It is a reward form for rewarding high-quality educational content creators and reading contributors in the BBT ecosystem. It is also a value tag for ecological circulation.
overview.zh: BBT是BBT生态发行的通用积分，是BBT生态体系内用于奖励优质教育内容创造者，及阅读贡献者的一种奖励形式，也是生态内流通的价值标的。
